name: CliKintoneTest-19 Should return the error message when incorrect authorization information (password)
fullName: features/common.feature#CliKintoneTest-19 Should return the error message when incorrect authorization information (password)

steps.name: Given Load username and password of user "user_for_common" as env vars: "USERNAME" and "PASSWORD"
When I run the command with args "record export --base-url $$TEST_KINTONE_BASE_URL --app 1 --username $USERNAME --password abc"
Then I should get the exit code is non-zero
And The output error message should match with the pattern: "\[401\] \[CB_WA01\] Password authentication failed."

labels.name: suite
labels.value: CliKintoneTest-19 Should return the error message when incorrect authorization information (password)
